<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
	<title>Document</title>
	<style>
	
		h1 {
			color: darkcyan;

		}
		#small {
			font-size: 10px;
		}

		#image {
			width: 200px;
			height: 200px;
		}

		#button {
			text-align: center;
			margin: 40px 0;
		}

	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Your password has been changed</h1>
	<hr>
	<div id="image" style="background-image: url('<%= images.link1 %>'); background-size:contain; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center;">			
	</div>
	<p>Hi <%= user.firstname + ' ' + user.lastname %>, we noted that your password account has been recently changed.</p>
	<p>If you didn't ask to change your password, please enter our website login page and reset your password immediatly.</p>
	<div id="button"><!--[if mso]>
			<v:roundrect xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" href="http://" style="height:53px;v-text-anchor:middle;width:200px;" arcsize="8%" stroke="f" fill="t">
			  <v:fill type="tile" src=""https://imgur.com/5BIp9d0.gif"" color="#49a9ce" />
			  <w:anchorlock/>
			  <center style="color:#ffffff;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;">Verify my email address</center>
			</v:roundrect>
		  <![endif]--><a href=<%= loginLink %> style="background-color:#49a9ce;background-image:url('https://imgur.com/5BIp9d0.gif');border-radius:4px;color:#ffffff;display:inline-block;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;line-height:53px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;width:200px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;mso-hide:all;">Login</a>
		 
	</div>
	<p>If you changed your password, then you can safely ignore this email.</p>
	<p>Cheers,</p>
	<h3><%= company.name %></h3>
	<hr>
	<p id="small">This message was sent to you by <%= company.name %></p>
</body>
</html>